show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Betrayed by her father and nearly assaulted by his boss, Khushi escapes and finds safety in the arms of Aarav, a powerful yet kind man. As love blossoms, secrets, lies, and betrayal threaten to tear them apart. Fighting for her dignity, dreams, and unborn child, Khushi rises against all odds—reclaiming her identity, uncovering her true roots, and finding love that lasts.
